{"tid":1305134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［認真］傾唔掂數唔撚買寶礦力","createTime":"2019-07-10T19:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T20:38:24.000Z","uid":217553,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d6ce1e87ae987bdc9d1a69c4ef2eecb154fbd1dd","tid":1305134,"uid":217553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:24:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">死線呢？要訂死線話比政府知佢地要做野</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家仲記唔記得文宣圖講緊抗爭既步驟，和理非既下一步係咩？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">依加有晒遊行時間表又有處處開花既連儂牆，<br />\n咁死線呢？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n見到個遊行時間表排撚到月尾，好多淺黃或者中立都理撚得你或者得閒先出，ig已經日日係到飲飲食食，話撚知你排到下年都未必引到好大關注，咁不如係各區遊行中間加插一日死線，再集中煲大佢，等大家唔好淡左件事先<br />\n<br />\n同埋經過幾次遊行，政府都冇撚理過我地，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要話比政府知佢地係要回應我地既訴求，而唔係次次遊行都龜縮係屋企食花生咁睇完就算</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔係話遊行同連儂牆冇用，兩個都好撚重要，至於守唔守連儂牆就唔係到討論，因為唔係呢個post既重點<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">死線可以話比政府知我地要佢地回應訴求，亦可以話比人知我地既行動係因為政府唔回應，係官迫民反，你唔訂條死線出黎仆街政府係唔撚會理你</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢上次都冇撚理到，但我地既行動就變左言之有理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">至於死線定幾時真係爭靠大家討論出黎，因為冇大台唔係一個人企出黎講就定到，所以真係想大家比d意見</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次死線冇記錯主要係政總現場再加tg投票既共識，但最近冇野餐，希望大家係到比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傾掂左下次遊行或者野餐買幾箱寶礦力比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申 cd rom左好耐 第一次開post 文筆又唔好 有錯屌細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8da6edfc4997483cc8b1b87a680d15b0d22fcc","tid":1305134,"uid":217553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:25:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cac9b99b326fb370f9588d723606f881b03b1975","tid":1305134,"uid":217553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc8da6edfc4997483cc8b1b87a680d15b0d22fcc","tid":1305134,"uid":217553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:25:28.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:25:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f31256aff477f12f2065c876dbabb73db8714be","tid":1305134,"uid":217553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cac9b99b326fb370f9588d723606f881b03b1975","tid":1305134,"uid":217553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc8da6edfc4997483cc8b1b87a680d15b0d22fcc","tid":1305134,"uid":217553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:25:28.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:25:38.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:25:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8fd0a149e03552ed78a36f14b6974692c4ef501f","tid":1305134,"uid":217553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f31256aff477f12f2065c876dbabb73db8714be","tid":1305134,"uid":217553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cac9b99b326fb370f9588d723606f881b03b1975","tid":1305134,"uid":217553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc8da6edfc4997483cc8b1b87a680d15b0d22fcc","tid":1305134,"uid":217553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:25:28.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:25:38.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:25:55.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:26:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed598bff09302fc8f12b131a091a4eb35cc63641","tid":1305134,"uid":217553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T19:27:18.000Z","msg":"咩意見都可以講下咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets